summary:
You can place freely actors.
This is also possible to make the actor sink and float.
descriptionHtml:
You can place freely actors for screen shots.
This is also possible to make the actor sink and float.

[b]Require:[/b]
[url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]Skyrim Script Extender (SKSE)[/url]

[b]Installation:[/b]
Unpack the contents to your Skyrim data folder.

[b]How to use:[/b]
Please equip the ring that has been added at the start of the game.

[b]Versions:[/b]
0.1 - Initial
author: anano
